Citation.sAbstract: Isobaric vapor liquid equilibria data have been determined at 101.3 kPa for the binary mixtures of (2,3-butanediol + n-butanol), (2,3-  butanediol + ethyl acetate) and (2,3-butanediol + butyl acetate). Thermodynamic consistency has been tested for all vapor liquid equilibria data.  The non-ideality of the vapor phase has been considered by using Hayden O Connell equation. The activity coefficients have been correlated  satisfactorily with Margules, Wilson, NRTL, and UNIQUAC models.
Citation.sTitle: Vapor liquid equilibria for the binary mixtures of 2,3-butanediol with n-butanol, n-butyl acetate, and ethyl acetate at 101.3 kPa
